V 391
Reworked directive API.  Added ``Body.parse_directive()``, ``.parse_directive_options()``, ``.parse_directive_arguments()`` methods.Added ``ExtensionOptions`` class, to parse directive options without parsing field bodies.  Factored ``Body.parse_field_body()`` out of ``Body.field()``, overridden in ``ExtensionOptions``.Generalized some state transition return values (``next_state``).

